title: DJ Envy likes what??
itunes:title: DJ Envy likes what??
description:
Thursday 10/26- Today on the show after DJ Envy was the number one trending topic on Twitter all because of a rumor coming out about him liking a certain sexual pleasure, that is all they had to talk about. In fact, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to DJ Envy for it. Moreover, they skipped over "Ask Yee" and decided to do "Breakfast Club Court" to get to the bottom.. or the top of this DJ Envy scandal.
